AssetCacheAgent(8) System Manager's Manual AssetCacheAgent(8)

NAME

AssetCacheAgent — Caching service agent

SYNOPSIS

AssetCacheAgent

DESCRIPTION

AssetCacheAgent displays notifications from the macOS caching service.

There are no configuration options to AssetCacheAgent. Users should not run AssetCacheAgent manually.

DIAGNOSTICS

AssetCacheAgent logs to the os_log(3) subsystem com.apple.AssetCache category Agent.

SEE ALSO

log(1), AssetCache(8)
